Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:34.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Torrent
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now that Kiriyama\Nhas joined us, shall we continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I set up the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, in the Lion King\Nchallenger's tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is what the board looked like when I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This just bothered me suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:02:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a9}Tokyo\NNagano\NTokushima\NKyoto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This weekend, I have to head to Tokushima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}So I felt like delving into one of my defeats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, continuing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black should go 6-a-Bishop,\Nand white should go 5-b-Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then black should go 7-d-Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black just needs to go 7-d-Pawn.\NWhy does the bishop need to be taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the type who gets killed on a battlefield\Nright away from moving around too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pffft!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Mr. Shigeta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sit there with pride\Nwhile constantly checking the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and before you know it,\Nyou're surrounded. The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like the Battle of Sekigahara's Shimazu type?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If black goes 6-a-Bishop, and white\Ngoes 5-b-Pawn, it'll just be a hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The 6-a-Bishop being taken is a benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever takes a Bishop first will degenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black going with 7-d-Pawn is logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Black Cat Team
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If black goes 7-d-Pawn and 6-d-Gold,\Nit's illogical to go with 6-a-Bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:12.61,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble\NRumble\NRumble
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It makes more sense to go 3-e-Pawn\Nto take your 7-a-Bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}White Cat Team
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll leave my 5-b-Pawn alone with your\N5-h-Rook open? Their future sure looks bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:21.95,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chuckle\NChuckle\NChuckle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, how about my 6-a-Bishop\Ntakes your 6-d-Gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'd approach my gold\Nwhen you can't even take the 7-d-Pawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}There are many words here, so we're providing\Nmetaphorical images as accompaniment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you let me take your 5-b-Pawn,\NI've already won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about 4-g-Bishop takes the 7-d-Pawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just use the 5-f-Pawn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't even get that?\NWhy don't you start over from the 1st dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Checkmate within 45 Moves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.44,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captured Piece:\NSilver
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Silence...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've finally quieted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:09.70,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stare
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:09.70,CenterSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate\Nwithin 7 Moves
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trick to quiet down hyper students in a classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}So this method still works, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Once you've solved it, take your seat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think about this, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you go for the 6-a-Bishop?\NOr the 7-d-Pawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, it's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once the board gets to this position,\Nyou're already in bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Don't undermine the premise.\NWe can't learn anything that way, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But unless we imagine it in the context of\Na real game, there's no point in studying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something would have to be done\Nbefore the board got to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be specific. How do you figure this is hopeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean explain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... How can I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's disturbing... or like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Disturbing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Disturbing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, did you want to say something\Nabstract, and think we'd interpret it as genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speak clearly! Or do you want me to\Nstimulate your speech center?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, put my cactus down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a workshop,\Nso verbalize your feelings for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, you studied alone,\Nso I'm sure you didn't bother with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But do your best, and go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... First...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The 3-g-Silver is still on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's one thing I find disturbing, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, in what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I think going with black's 7-d-Pawn\Nwill only result in injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Injury? No way, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yeah. At this point, I agree\Nwith the steamed bun's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Steamed bun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What's that, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna step outside?\NThat would make my day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, it's noisy. Shush it, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll smack you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Disturbing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I'll check my schedule and give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. After school, I don't have any plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Can you come back tomorrow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, just you."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what Mr. Shimada asked me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, the next day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you come continuously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wobble{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't slept?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have. Or more like, I passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to drink, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of it. What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Then hot coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I only have instant, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One more loss and the next one\Nwill be do-or-die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Straight losses...\NThat's the one thing I don't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have been wondering\Nif I get to play in my hometown or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First, I need two wins.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sixth match is in my hometown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, your hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yamagata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yamagata...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What's it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's just snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What about when there's no snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mountains, rivers, rice paddies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yeah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if there are rice paddies, that's not nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But they're reducing the acreage.\NEven now, those rice paddies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:09:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if I say this,\Nit's hard to understand, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's a place that\Ndoesn't want anything there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for people... and rice paddies...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Schools... and homes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't hear what he said,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a feeling he said, "That's exactly why."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, shall we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead an build the fortress normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You remember the board\Nfrom yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}8-h-King.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}9-e-Pawn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}3-h-Rook.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}7-c-Knight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}1-f-Pawn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}4-b-Bishop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}3-g-Silver.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}5-c-Silver.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}3-e-Pawn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's rushing towards me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Shimada's thoughts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like water that's been let loose from a dam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So suddenly, and so much force!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}3-e-Bishop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Same, Bishop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}4-c-Pawn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I was sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I could've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My shoulder and my eyes? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I think about it, it was the first time\NI was subjected{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to a Rank A player's thoughts\Nfor several hours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was like a muddy stream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I wouldn't let myself\Nbe swept away or retreat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I held on desperately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, we're both professionals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not a relationship where\Njust one person is allowed to benefit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Shimada thought I had something that\Nhe could "steal," which is why he invited me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And though possibly minor,\NI thought I had something to offer,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that's why I asked to join\Nthe workshop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because on that day,\Na thought pierced my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"There's something I want to ask him."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until I get that answer, all I can do is hang on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Shimada left to Tokushima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The curtain was about to lift...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}on the third match\Nof the Lion King Tournament.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.00,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Torrent
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:21.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Passing Time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Report Card
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just barely made it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.02,CenterSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,End-of-Year Party
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess everyone's going to Mouseland\Nin two days for an End-of-Year party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although I wasn't invited, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know why you keep informing me\Nof these things throughout the year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really think this falls\Ninto the realm of bullying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Seriously?\N- Come on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I squeaked by with attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't join a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My rank is stagnant, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't accomplished anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was able to move up a grade because of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, Mr. Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't accomplished anything?\NDon't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been coming to school while working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You make your own meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You do the laundry, take out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make money, pay rent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was 17, I thought,\N"I can be a big shot when I grow up."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had that groundless dream\Nwhile going to the arcade, reading manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,hanging out with friends, watching TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never worried about rent\Nor bothered to save up money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never cleaned or prepared meals\Nor did the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:22.88,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi!\NI need\Nto vacuum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So don't tell me\Nyou haven't accomplished anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want him to stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's always like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Insensitive, outspoken...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just wish he would stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When he suddenly says things like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I can't handle it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. It's still cold outside, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about we go for some oden?\NMy treat, to celebrate you advancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. You don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you wanna go? To Mouseland?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just us two guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. Oden...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, oden is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my short spring vacation began.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Lion King Tournament,\Nmatch three, day two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Lion King Tournament\NLive Feed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Shimada is in a tight spot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this rate, all he can do is persevere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On top of that, Mr. Shimada\Nhas expended more time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:17:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One more loss and the next one\Nwill be do-or-die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Straight losses...\NThat's the one thing I don't want.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Mr. Shimada... Please... Please...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hina, and Momo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, w-we came to pick up our empty boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:35.26,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tiny
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.26,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glance\NGlance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I serve guests?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure tea would be fine for adults,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but what do I serve a middle school student\Nand a kindergartener?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}You have hot tea with inari sushi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Don't you have any chocolate?\NServe me something sweet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:18:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, relatively easy to serve as a guest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}You don't have any soda?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Um... Thank you for\Nthe multi-tiered box of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Did you eat all of it, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I-I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nom\NNom\NNom
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though she ate most of it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I managed to have two pieces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the one with wasabi was really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis and I made that together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It turned out really well for Girls' Day,\Nso we made some for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa likes wasabi,\Nso we put that in for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:18:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we last saw you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who was that person with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:07.48,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stare\NStare
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... from that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... How can I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I was wondering if you were all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, because it looked like\Nyou were arguing with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it seemed like you were\Non the receiving end...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-So I wondered if you were okay, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is she a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I really were a witch,\NI wouldn't have such pathetic hardships.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. No, she's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's no witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We're family, so sometimes we fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all right. Because we're siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same at your house, right, Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's true! Akari and Hina\Nare always fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She really cries a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still, really close!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're home! Mystery solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, that woman is Rei's sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief!\NI was worried over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was just an argument between siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've figured?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:21:00.59,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, Hina, that's probably worse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:04.84,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heap
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- Warm.\N- This is the best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:04.84,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cozy\NCozy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch Squirrely Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's watch Squirrely Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm hungry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Teach us, Squirrely Teacher!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Squirrely Teacher! Squirrely Teacher!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mreow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I'm hungry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Squirrely Teacher, please teach us something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Never mind that squirrel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}In fact, I'm so hungry,\NI could eat that squirrel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't eat squirrels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Teacher knows everything{\i0}
